snippet.title: Yanga! TV
snippet.description:
Dynamic, irreverent, effervescent, welcome to YANGA! – a new general entertainment destination, launching New Year 2018, giving voice to Africa’s thriving diaspora. Echoing the continent’s bold and beautiful style, YANGA! brings Africa’s energy with content featuring its best entertainers, comedians and musicians. YANGA! will offer viewers a taste of home with positive and inspirational stories to celebrate the cultural richness and pride of Africa and its people. YANGA!

Find us on Sky Channel 186 and Freesat Channel 171.
